oai_dc:dc.dc:title: MBA Graduates
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Students
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The first class of MBA students at Christian Brothers University stand ready to graduate. The MBA program began in 1989; the first cohort graduated in 1991: Paul Anthony Catanzaro, Raymond Ronald Chapman, Thomas Jackson Dempsey, Thomas H. Lawrence III, Tawana Parker, Charles Franklin Roberts III, Timothy Colin Threlkeld, Alan Kenneth Wells, Rolland W. Young Jr.
